    <h1>About Play UNO Free</h1>
    <p class="page-subtitle">The story behind the best browser-based UNO game.</p>

    <h2>Our Mission</h2>
    <p>We believe playing card games with friends should be effortless. No app store downloads, no account signups, no paywalls. Just open a link and play — on any device, anywhere in the world.</p>

    <h2>What Makes Us Different</h2>
    <p>Most online UNO games cap at 4 players. We built Play UNO Free to support <strong>up to 20 players</strong> in a single room, making it the go-to choice for large friend groups, classrooms, Discord communities, and family reunions. And it's 100% free forever.</p>

    <p>Our game features smooth, polished animations that rival native apps. The real-time multiplayer engine handles disconnections, reconnections, and even AFK players — so the game never gets stuck.</p>

    <h2>Built With Love</h2>
    <p>Play UNO Free is an indie project built by a passionate developer. The game is constantly being improved with new features, better performance, and community feedback.</p>

    <h2>Tech Stack</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Frontend:</strong> HTML5 Canvas, vanilla JavaScript</li>
      <li><strong>Backend:</strong> Node.js, Express, Socket.io</li>
      <li><strong>Real-time:</strong> WebSockets for instant multiplayer</li>
    </ul>

